            <td style='font-size:12px;padding-left:10px;'><p><strong class="BoldAndBlue">Kandy</strong> - a lovely exotic city, the Hill Capital and last stronghold of the Sinhala Kings is a UNESCO World Heritage Site which retains an aura of grandeur, time has not affected. Encircled by hills,
